    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring a high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, the powertrain delivers linear thrust paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. Clad in original Carbon Black metallic, the exterior retains its factory luster, while the interior showcases immaculate Nappa leather with firm bolsters and zero pixel degradation in the instrument cluster. A turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning purist who values mechanical integrity and historical authenticity.",
