    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that can only be described as a showroom-quality time capsule. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and its condition reflects a level of care rarely seen. The exterior paint finish is absolutely flawless, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory gloss with zero stone chips, swirl marks, or scratches. All body panels are perfectly aligned, and the original alloy wheels are pristine, without a hint of curb rash. Inside, the interior remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather seats are firm and supple with no visible wear on the bolsters, and the carpets have been protected by factory mats since delivery. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, backed by a comprehensive, folder-bound service history from authorized specialists. The engine bay is detailed and dry, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, having never been exposed to inclement weather. This is a collector-grade vehicle suited for the most discerning buyer who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
